channel.title: RoxoScape 317 Economy Server
channel.description:
Hey guys i wanted to show you guys RoxoScape. Im in the development process so sadly i do not have a website as of right now. But that doesn't mean u guys can't join! Here is a video so you can see what its all about! Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ngy6eXrukCI&feature=youtu.be Download link: https://www.dropbox.com/s/2mily59foodhvd3/RoxoScape%20Client.rar?dl=0
Hope to see you online!
To start playing you need winrar. once u have winrar, open the folder you downloaded and click extract on the folder. then click on start roxoscape. then you should be ready to play! if you get, "GUI Java is not recognized as an internal or external command, operable program or batch file." then make sure you have jdk1.8.0_25 then make sure that is in you path under environment variables. see you online!
